
# DP on Subsequences Pattern

## Subsequence DP ke 10 Main Variants:

| Variant | Description | Approach |
|---------|-------------|----------|
| **Subset Sum** | Does subset sum to target? | Take or skip |
| **Count Subsets with Sum** | Count subsets summing to target | Take + skip counting |
| **Minimum Subset Sum Difference** | Partition into two with min diff | Target = sum/2 |
| **Equal Sum Partition** | Can array be split into equal sum | Target = sum/2 |
| **Target Sum (+/-)** | Assign + or - to reach target | P - N = target |
| **Number of Subsequences with Sum** | Count subsequences with given sum | Take/skip with modulo |
| **Largest Divisible Subset** | Every pair divisible | Sort + LIS |
| **Longest Increasing Subsequence** | Strictly increasing | Pick/skip with prev |
| **Number of Longest Increasing Subseq** | Count of LIS | Pair (len, count) |
| **Maximum Sum Increasing Subseq** | Max sum instead of length | Sum aggregation |

