## 📝 Key Formulas to Remember

| Operation | Formula |
|-----------|---------|
| Subset Sum Exists | `dp[i][t] = dp[i+1][t] OR dp[i+1][t-nums[i]]` |
| Count Subsets | `dp[i][t] = dp[i+1][t] + dp[i+1][t-nums[i]]` |
| LIS Length | `dp[i] = 1 + max(dp[j]) for j < i and nums[j] < nums[i]` |
| LIS Count | `count[i] = sum(count[j]) for j with max length` |
| Target Sum | `P = (target + sum)/2, then subset sum count` |
| XOR | `dp[i][x] = dp[i+1][x] + dp[i+1][x^nums[i]]` |

